---
title: Roast Thyme Chicken with Lemon, Quick Potato Hash and Chive Crema
description: Super simple to throw together and packed with flavour, this thyme and lemon chicken is a star. The crispy potato hash and tender green beans are complemented perfectly with a tasty dollop of chive sour cream. Best part? It will all be on your plate in no time!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/roast-thyme-chicken-12608f06.jpg
